data.name: SearchCounter
data.description: A Flask based application that takes multiple paragraphs of text as input and assigns a unique id to each paragraph and stores words to paragraph mapping on an inverted index. Given a word, it then returns the top paragraphs that contain that word in order of frequency of the word.

data.name: Blog-It
data.description: Basic CRUD functionality based blogging website where users can go and post, edit and delete post. Other features include sign-up facility for new users, comment on other blog posts.
